dialog.body: Hello! Thank you for calling Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Jordan Lewis. May I have your name, please?
Hi, my name is Cynthia Roberts.
Nice to meet you, Cynthia! How can I assist you today?
I need to file a new claim after a recent incident.
Of course, Cynthia. Can you provide me with the date of the incident and a brief description of what happened?
The incident occurred on the fifth of October and involved a minor fender bender.
Thank you, Cynthia. We will process your claim accordingly. Could you also provide me with the make and model of your vehicle, as well as your current policy number?
My vehicle is a two zero one nine Toyota Corolla, and my policy number is A B C one two three four.
Great. Thank you for sharing that information, Cynthia. We will be in touch with you regarding the next steps. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
No, that's all for now. Thank you, Jordan.
You're welcome, Cynthia. Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. Have a great day!
